{"issue":{"id":775,"project":{"id":16,"name":"easySDI"},"tracker":{"id":2,"name":"Feature"},"status":{"id":9,"name":"Accepted"},"priority":{"id":5,"name":"High"},"author":{"id":3,"name":"Magoni Bruno"},"category":{"id":12,"name":"CORE"},"fixed_version":{"id":114,"name":"Unplanned"},"subject":"On Update Cascading Action","description":"Having a look of easySDI database structure, quite all constraints have got no action attached to ON UPDATE event!\r\nIt is very important to define CASCADE action to such event to guaranty data coherence if technical id have to change (i.e. for data migration, for future easySDI changes in sys tables content, and so on...).\r\n\r\nSo all relations constraint must be altered (in fact removed and recreated) for ON UPDATE event to attach CASCADE action.\r\n","done_ratio":0,"custom_fields":[{"id":3,"name":"Sponsor","multiple":true,"value":[]},{"id":4,"name":"Functional impact"},{"id":5,"name":"Ergonomic impact"}],"created_on":"2014-07-17T18:34:49Z","updated_on":"2015-03-06T22:07:19Z","journals":[{"id":3836,"user":{"id":3,"name":"Magoni Bruno"},"created_on":"2014-07-17T19:55:01Z","details":[{"property":"attr","name":"category_id","new_value":"12"}]},{"id":3904,"user":{"id":9,"name":"M\u00e9rour Xavier"},"notes":"It's a very good thing to have an even more robut solution and be sure we keep integrity in the whole data model.\r\n\r\n+1 for me.","created_on":"2014-07-28T13:15:41Z","details":[]},{"id":3947,"user":{"id":3,"name":"Magoni Bruno"},"created_on":"2014-08-03T17:41:15Z","details":[{"property":"attr","name":"assigned_to_id","new_value":"282"}]},{"id":4074,"user":{"id":3,"name":"Magoni Bruno"},"notes":"+1","created_on":"2014-09-02T09:23:59Z","details":[]},{"id":4083,"user":{"id":777,"name":"Teixeira J\u00e9r\u00f4me"},"notes":"+1","created_on":"2014-09-03T11:34:49Z","details":[]},{"id":4177,"user":{"id":3,"name":"Magoni Bruno"},"notes":"","created_on":"2014-10-07T10:08:02Z","details":[{"property":"attr","name":"status_id","old_value":"1